<h2>Follow LT on twitter</h2>
<p>
I tweet about site status, and news, sometimes tips. Traffic pretty low (couple per months). I also sometimes do direct help by mean of @replies. I'm <a href="http://twitter.com/loudtweeter">loudtweeter</a>.
