<h2>Credits</h2>
<p>
[% |loc %]
This site is born from a need that <a href="http://loiclemeur.com">Loic Le Meur</a> first expressed. He wanted his tweets on his <a href="http://typepad.com">TypePad</a> blog.
[% END %]
<p>
So, he asked me, If I could develop a tool for him. Eventually, I turned the tool into a site as more people were interested by this kind of service.
</p>
